						<summary>

						<p>On a fragment of a stone near the Īśvara temple.</p>						

						<p>Circa 12th century.</p>						

						<p>It seems to record a gift of land, oil, etc., made in favour of a deity and a house-site to the <hi rend="italic">sthānapati</hi> Sarvvēśvara-paṇḍita. The record is damaged.</p>						

